Calling all baseball lovers!
Check out Kacaron's new custom keychains. You can create your custom keyring with your name, of course with your favorite player's name, too.
It is very versatile, it can go with any style - Keychain, Bag Charm, Name Tag, etc.
Perfect gifts for baseball lovers and fans!


-Personalized Name: Max 10 characters, UPPERCASE ONLY, No special characters
-made of hard plastic (PLA filament)
-3d printed products: visible layer lines on the products
-Dimensions: e.g. (In case of SEBASTIAN: 4.95L * 1.03H * 0.23T inch / In case of AVA: 2.68L * 1.03H * 0.23T inch)
-Returns not accepted
